  <brief_title>Probiotic in Treatment of Adult Patients With Drug-resistant Epilepsy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Investigation of Probiotic Effect on Seizure Frequency of Adult Patients With Drug-resistant Epilepsy; A Randomized Double-blind Parallel Placebo-controlled Clinical Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
