  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is a randomized, double-blind parallel group placebo-controlled clinical trial&#xD;
      with the aim of investigating the effect of probiotic versus placebo on drug-resistant adult&#xD;
      patients with epilepsy.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
